# Copy to .env.local and set per environment.

# When set, the catch-all routes under /api/{quotation,issuance,policy-admin}
# proxy to this URL instead of returning local mock data. Leave unset for
# pure mock mode (the default — what most local development uses).
#
# UI-only routes (awaiting-approval, pending-breakdown, proposal-scoped
# /members shortcut) keep using the local dispatcher even in proxy mode —
# see src/lib/api-mock/group-pas/http.ts MOCK_ONLY_PATTERNS.
#
# GROUP_PAS_BACKEND_URL=https://group-pas-dev.anairacloud.com
